🔹 Q2) Write a function which will accept the name of the hospital and calculate the average charges of doctors visiting that hospital.


---

✅ Function

CREATE OR REPLACE FUNCTION avg_charges(hname VARCHAR)
RETURNS NUMERIC AS
$$
DECLARE
    avg_val NUMERIC;
BEGIN
    SELECT AVG(d.charges) INTO avg_val
    FROM doctor d
    JOIN hospital h ON d.h_no = h.h_no
    WHERE h.h_name = hname;

    RETURN avg_val;
END;
$$ LANGUAGE plpgsql;


---

✅ Call

